It was...

626
00:41:04,765 --> 00:41:09,169
Seize Song Seo In
and his servant Soeddung immediately.

627
00:41:10,804 --> 00:41:11,672
My Lord.

628
00:41:16,844 --> 00:41:17,678
Wait.

629
00:41:23,517 --> 00:41:26,053
My Lord, why are you doing this?

630
00:41:26,053 --> 00:41:29,756
Last May in Ikcheon,
Ok Tae Young met them

631
00:41:29,756 --> 00:41:32,593
and conspired to murder
her runaway husband, Seong Yun Gyeom.

632
00:41:33,460 --> 00:41:34,862
- What?
- Interrogate them.

633
00:41:34,862 --> 00:41:36,363
Wait.

634
00:41:41,869 --> 00:41:42,736
Wait.

635
00:41:50,544 --> 00:41:51,445
My Lord.

636
00:41:55,315 --> 00:41:57,451
Soeddung, servant of Song Seo In

637
00:41:58,051 --> 00:41:59,887
hired Ok Tae Young for legal advocacy

638
00:41:59,887 --> 00:42:02,322
and summoned her to Ikcheon.

639
00:42:02,623 --> 00:42:06,226
