"The Investigator and the Maiden."

657
00:43:27,407 --> 00:43:28,308
You!

658
00:43:28,308 --> 00:43:30,511
Shut your darn mouth!

659
00:43:30,511 --> 00:43:33,514
That man is no mere servant.

660
00:43:33,514 --> 00:43:36,550
