and even lived with them.

662
00:43:39,820 --> 00:43:40,754
How can she claim ignorance?

663
00:43:42,089 --> 00:43:44,558
Do you still insist you do not know him?

664
00:43:56,069 --> 00:43:56,904
My Lord!

665
00:43:57,404 --> 00:43:58,972
Soeddung is innocent.

666
00:43:58,972 --> 00:44:01,341
He only followed my orders.

667
00:44:01,341 --> 00:44:03,777
