671
00:44:09,183 --> 00:44:12,519
It was because the ship was damaged,
and I couldn't leave, My Lord.

672
00:44:14,621 --> 00:44:17,024
As for Seol Rang,
he was accused of theft.

673
00:44:17,024 --> 00:44:18,425
So he is slandering us.

674
00:44:23,397 --> 00:44:24,231
Man Seok.

675
00:44:25,599 --> 00:44:26,567
Man Seok!

676
00:44:31,505 --> 00:44:33,507
Man Seok.

677
00:44:33,874 --> 00:44:34,942
My Lord, please.

678
00:44:34,942 --> 00:44:36,877
How can knowing each other prove

679
00:44:36,877 --> 00:44:39,580
a plot to murder Seong Yun Gyeom?

680
00:44:40,147 --> 00:44:43,050
How could you deceive me so?

681
00:44:43,050 --> 00:44:44,284
Please believe me.

682
00:44:45,452 --> 00:44:48,021
I didn't kill my husband.

683
00:44:49,890 --> 00:44:50,891
