695
00:45:20,153 --> 00:45:22,022
So I asked him to act as my husband.

696
00:45:22,389 --> 00:45:24,825
I never killed my husband.

697
00:45:25,158 --> 00:45:28,262
Please, I beg you to believe me.

698
00:45:28,662 --> 00:45:31,265
You have already lied to me.

699
00:45:33,066 --> 00:45:35,869
Every of your word has lost
credibility here.

700
00:45:36,470 --> 00:45:37,471
My Lord!

701
00:45:41,508 --> 00:45:43,544
My Lord! I will explain everything.

702
00:45:43,544 --> 00:45:44,711
It was me, My Lord.

703
00:45:44,711 --> 00:45:46,213
I killed him!

704
00:45:53,854 --> 00:45:57,191
When Deputy Tribunal Officer Seong
came looking for Seong Yun Gyeom,

705
00:45:57,991 --> 00:46:02,763
I was enraged at him
for abandoning his wife for seven years.

706
00:46:02,763 --> 00:46:04,798
When I met him in Qing,

707
00:46:04,798 --> 00:46:06,667
I urged him to return to his wife,

708
00:46:07,167 --> 00:46:08,402
but he refused.

709
00:46:09,069 --> 00:46:11,071
So I killed him with my own hands.

710
00:46:12,539 --> 00:46:15,042
No, that is not true.

711
00:46:15,042 --> 00:46:16,043
I...

712
00:46:17,878 --> 00:46:19,546
I was deeply in love with her.

713
00:46:20,948 --> 00:46:24,484
I wanted to live as her husband,
at least for a single day.

714
00:46:24,852 --> 00:46:27,087
To hear her call me her husband once,

715
00:46:27,387 --> 00:46:29,456
I deceived everyone. It was all me.

716
00:46:32,693 --> 00:46:34,428
Yun Gyeom.

717
00:46:34,428 --> 00:46:35,429
I am sorry.

718
00:46:36,363 --> 00:46:37,631
It was all my selfishness.

719
00:46:38,465 --> 00:46:39,366
So,

720
00:46:40,534 --> 00:46:45,839
