or

734
00:47:59,980 --> 00:48:02,516
are you Kim Nak Soo's servant, Goodeoki?

735
00:48:15,095 --> 00:48:17,998
I am asking you, what is your name?

736
00:48:24,471 --> 00:48:25,539
My name is...

737
00:48:36,316 --> 00:48:37,384
Bring him here.

738
