Man Seok.

797
00:54:31,672 --> 00:54:34,741
Man Seok.

798
00:54:35,108 --> 00:54:36,944
Man Seok.

799
00:54:43,483 --> 00:54:46,587
Man Seok, answer me.

800
00:54:52,192 --> 00:54:54,528
Man Seok.

801
00:54:55,195 --> 00:54:59,032
Man Seok, I am sorry.

802
00:55:06,640 --> 00:55:10,344
After reviewing evidence and testimonies,
Song Seo In is found guilty

803
00:55:10,777 --> 00:55:14,882
of killing Seong Yun Gyeom,
impersonating his identity,

804
00:55:15,315 --> 00:55:19,086
and violating royal orders
by faking his death.

805
00:55:19,820 --> 00:55:21,154
He is sentenced to execution.

806
00:55:30,264 --> 00:55:34,034
The servant Goodeoki is clearly guilty
of harming her master and fleeing.

807
00:55:34,568 --> 00:55:37,804
And she is guilty of impersonating
the noble Ok Tae Young.

808
00:55:38,539 --> 00:55:40,674
She deserves execution.

809
00:55:41,975 --> 00:55:42,809
However,

810
00:55:43,844 --> 00:55:47,481
considering her service
as a legal advocate aiding many people,

811
00:55:48,549 --> 00:55:51,785
she shall be returned
to her owner, Kim So Hye.

812
00:56:52,479 --> 00:56:53,547
Where is my father?

813
00:56:54,014 --> 00:56:55,949
Do you think I will let you see him?

814
00:56:56,316 --> 00:56:58,252
Because of you, my father is dead.

815
00:57:02,389 --> 00:57:03,290
Right!

816
00:57:05,259 --> 00:57:06,260
I heard you are pregnant.

817
00:57:08,095 --> 00:57:11,198
Then that child is mine as well, right?

818
00:57:15,502 --> 00:57:17,471
Welcome home, Goodeoki.

819
00:57:28,282 --> 00:57:32,085
Do you resent me?

820
00:57:36,290 --> 00:57:38,926
Despite tarnishing
the Royal Tribunal's authority,

821
00:57:40,227 --> 00:57:44,097
I am truly grateful
you spared my sister-in-law, My Lord.

822
00:57:45,966 --> 00:57:48,302
Saving Legal Advocate Ok

823
00:57:48,302 --> 00:57:50,103
despite opposition

824
00:57:51,338 --> 00:57:52,973
was the King's decision.

825
00:57:54,374 --> 00:57:57,711
If you were unaware she was a slave,

826
00:58:00,013 --> 00:58:01,782
you must have been as shocked as I was.

827
00:58:07,955 --> 00:58:09,289
I apologize,

828
00:58:10,891 --> 00:58:15,128
but she is like a mother to me,
regardless of status.

829
00:58:18,265 --> 00:58:20,200
She took me in when I had nowhere to go,

830
00:58:22,169 --> 00:58:24,404
and rebuilt a broken family.

831
00:58:31,311 --> 00:58:32,846
Though guilty of crimes,

832
00:58:34,181 --> 00:58:35,249
I cannot

833
00:58:37,317 --> 00:58:39,286
blame her.

834
00:59:19,526 --> 00:59:20,661
Geumbok.

835
00:59:21,361 --> 00:59:23,630
They asked me to move these herbs
to the storage.

836
00:59:23,630 --> 00:59:24,932
I just stepped in briefly.

837
00:59:26,233 --> 00:59:27,334
What about my father?

838
00:59:28,035 --> 00:59:29,303
He is safe in another shed.

839
00:59:29,303 --> 00:59:31,438
Don't worry about him.

840
00:59:32,139 --> 00:59:33,173
Where...

841
00:59:34,208 --> 00:59:35,776
Where was he hiding all this time?

842
00:59:35,776 --> 00:59:38,378
He said he lived in a secluded temple.

843
00:59:38,679 --> 00:59:41,815
He ate well,
and even recovered from his illness.

844
00:59:42,850 --> 00:59:45,018
He has been here for a while,

845
00:59:45,352 --> 00:59:48,155
but they locked him in another house,
afraid we might find out.

846
00:59:48,722 --> 00:59:50,891
- Is that so?
- Don't worry too much.

847
00:59:50,891 --> 00:59:52,993
They won't dare harm him now.

848
00:59:54,394 --> 00:59:56,964
Deputy Tribunal Officer's family
frequently sends people

849
00:59:56,964 --> 00:59:59,066
to patrol outside the house.

850
01:00:00,133 --> 01:00:04,071
It has the Minister of Taxation on edge.

851
01:00:05,606 --> 01:00:06,640
Why?

852
01:00:06,640 --> 01:00:09,910
Is it not obvious?
This is Bak Jun Gi's secret storage.

853
01:00:10,577 --> 01:00:12,546
The herbs he stores here
are made into pills

854
01:00:12,546 --> 01:00:15,115
in the back warehouse and sold.

855
01:00:16,884 --> 01:00:20,787
But what is that herb?
It smells so fishy.

856
01:00:22,623 --> 01:00:24,691
So that is why they needed aloe.

857
01:00:28,395 --> 01:00:31,198
Why did you go to the Royal Tribunal
without permission?

858
01:00:31,198 --> 01:00:33,867
I was frustrated by all the delays!

859
01:00:33,867 --> 01:00:35,669
I told you there was a reason for this!

860
01:00:35,669 --> 01:00:37,871
What reason?
You have the diseased village.

861
01:00:37,871 --> 01:00:39,773
What more are you hiding?

862
01:00:40,941 --> 01:00:43,143
If you act without my approval again,

863
01:00:43,977 --> 01:00:45,345
you will end up like your father.

864
01:01:06,300 --> 01:01:07,267
Yun Gyeom.

865
01:01:09,203 --> 01:01:12,840
So, did you recover Man Seok's body?

866
01:01:14,241 --> 01:01:18,145
Yes, we retrieved it
outside the city gates.

867
01:01:24,284 --> 01:01:25,219
Thank you.

868
01:01:26,820 --> 01:01:29,923
Bury him in a sunny spot
in Cheongsu County.

869
01:01:31,325 --> 01:01:32,259
That guy

870
01:01:33,560 --> 01:01:36,930
used to sing about wanting
to be buried in Cheongsu County.

871
01:01:38,966 --> 01:01:42,936
And prepare a spot next to him for me.

872
01:01:43,837 --> 01:01:46,139
I will need to join him
and keep him company.

873
01:01:46,139 --> 01:01:48,175
When I return from Cheongsu County,

874
01:01:48,175 --> 01:01:49,743
I will find a solution no matter what.

875
01:01:49,743 --> 01:01:53,480
You cannot bear this unjust
accusation of murder.

876
01:01:53,480 --> 01:01:54,515
What will you do?

877
01:01:55,215 --> 01:01:58,151
Will you search for your brother again?

878
01:01:58,151 --> 01:02:00,621
- Yes, if I must.
- It will be futile.

879
01:02:00,621 --> 01:02:03,690
I am already a traitor to the king.

880
01:02:04,525 --> 01:02:06,593
Stop worrying about me,

881
01:02:06,593 --> 01:02:07,995
and instead,

882
01:02:09,830 --> 01:02:11,498
protect your sister-in-law.

883
01:02:12,633 --> 01:02:15,435
This is my request to you.

884
01:02:23,443 --> 01:02:24,411
Take this.

885
01:02:25,445 --> 01:02:28,415
Deliver this to her.

886
01:02:34,655 --> 01:02:37,858
Madam So Hye insisted
you must not be entering the house.

887
01:02:42,963 --> 01:02:44,131
Why?

888
01:02:44,131 --> 01:02:47,067
Are you here to beg
for Goodeoki to be sold as well?

889
01:02:48,435 --> 01:02:52,105
You are not the kind of person
to show such generosity.

890
01:02:52,105 --> 01:02:54,775
Don't regret it after she dies.

891
01:02:55,175 --> 01:02:56,376
Watch your words.

892
01:02:59,746 --> 01:03:01,248
Let me meet her once,

893
01:03:02,816 --> 01:03:04,051
and I will keep this a secret.

894
01:03:05,252 --> 01:03:06,420
What secret?

895
01:03:06,420 --> 01:03:09,122
That a concubine dared to attend
the noblewomen's gatherings

896
01:03:09,122 --> 01:03:10,924
only to be turned away,

897
01:03:10,924 --> 01:03:14,294
and that you guard
Bak Jun Gi's storage like a dog.

898
01:03:15,762 --> 01:03:18,432
Must rumors of you being beaten
also spread?

899
01:03:22,970 --> 01:03:24,571
Fine, let us do this.

900
01:03:24,905 --> 01:03:28,075
It will be amusing to show you
her pitiful state.

901
01:03:28,075 --> 01:03:29,343
Why not?

902
01:03:44,958 --> 01:03:46,527
What brings you here?

903
01:03:53,700 --> 01:03:55,469
Your husband asked me
to deliver this to you.

904
01:04:01,041 --> 01:04:02,042
Surely...

905
01:04:04,278 --> 01:04:05,312
Not yet.

906
01:04:09,783 --> 01:04:11,285
Deputy Tribunal Officer Seong
and his wife

907
01:04:11,985 --> 01:04:14,354
have gone to Cheongsu County
for the servant's funeral.

908
01:04:19,726 --> 01:04:21,595
Will you just mourn like this?

909
01:04:24,431 --> 01:04:26,366
What more can I possibly do?

910
01:04:28,969 --> 01:04:30,470
I plan to hire someone

911
01:04:31,805 --> 01:04:33,373
to help you escape.

912
01:04:34,641 --> 01:04:35,676
Are you saying

913
01:04:37,511 --> 01:04:39,980
I have to become a runaway slave again?

914
01:04:39,980 --> 01:04:42,316
Will you follow your husband to death?

915
01:04:42,316 --> 01:04:43,317
Or

916
01:04:44,017 --> 01:04:46,286
will you let your child
live as a servant?

917
01:04:47,554 --> 01:04:50,557
Is that how you repay
those who sacrificed for you?

918
01:04:54,795 --> 01:04:58,298
Without the name Ok Tae Young,

919
01:04:59,700 --> 01:05:01,235
can you do nothing?

920
01:05:05,239 --> 01:05:08,242
Deok Hun's father, upon isolation,
said something.

921
01:05:08,976 --> 01:05:11,712
The fact that amidst
the chaos of disease,

922
01:05:13,280 --> 01:05:15,816
he made the infamous fraudulent couple
the talk of town

923
01:05:16,450 --> 01:05:17,985
reveals that Bak Jun Gi

924
01:05:19,353 --> 01:05:21,021
is hiding something.

925
01:05:22,022 --> 01:05:23,056
What?

926
01:05:23,056 --> 01:05:25,225
He diverted
the Royal Tribunal's attention

927
01:05:25,425 --> 01:05:27,828
just as he misled
the Magistrate Seong seven years ago.

928
01:05:31,231 --> 01:05:33,433
Just as he misled Father as well?

929
01:05:34,935 --> 01:05:38,005
You cannot end up exploited
like Magistrate Seong.

930
01:05:38,005 --> 01:05:39,706
You must escape here, somehow.

931
01:05:42,676 --> 01:05:47,047
Do you know the symptoms
of this strange disease?

932
01:06:05,799 --> 01:06:08,202
You pretended to be noble,
but look at you now.

933
01:06:08,902 --> 01:06:09,970
What was it?

934
01:06:10,237 --> 01:06:12,306
"This is our first meeting."

935
01:06:13,440 --> 01:06:16,376
"I am the eldest daughter-in-law
of the Cheongsu County's Seong family."

936
01:06:16,376 --> 01:06:18,078
"My name is Ok Tae Young."

937
01:06:19,046 --> 01:06:20,247
Ridiculous.

938
01:06:21,148 --> 01:06:23,250
How did you find out that Seo In and I

939
01:06:24,284 --> 01:06:25,519
were pretending to be a married couple?

940
01:06:25,986 --> 01:06:28,322
I followed you
when I heard you came to Hanyang

941
01:06:28,322 --> 01:06:29,489
to sell aloe.

942
01:06:33,594 --> 01:06:34,828
This here is

943
01:06:35,762 --> 01:06:37,130
my husband.

944
01:06:37,397 --> 01:06:39,800
I wanted to show him to you and boast.

945
01:06:40,868 --> 01:06:43,670
I saw you with Seo In
at your mother's grave.

946
01:06:43,670 --> 01:06:45,506
You shameless wench.

947
01:06:51,645 --> 01:06:52,579
How does it feel?

948
01:06:54,214 --> 01:06:56,216
A servant pretending to be noble,

949
01:06:56,216 --> 01:06:59,152
giving, helping, and showing mercy,
did you enjoy it?

950
01:07:00,354 --> 01:07:01,688
Of course, I did.

951
01:07:03,257 --> 01:07:05,058
I did many good things.

952
01:07:05,058 --> 01:07:06,960
That was all pretense.

953
01:07:06,960 --> 01:07:08,595
You are just a hypocrite.

954
01:07:08,595 --> 01:07:09,897
What is wrong with that?

955
01:07:11,598 --> 01:07:13,767
When the privileged show hypocrisy,

956
01:07:14,768 --> 01:07:17,204
at least, it allows the underprivileged
to breathe for a while.

957
01:07:17,204 --> 01:07:19,206
Do you think that makes you
a great person?

958
01:07:19,873 --> 01:07:21,041
A great person?

959
01:07:22,309 --> 01:07:23,277
No.

960
01:07:24,411 --> 01:07:26,647
I just wanted to be a human.

961
01:07:28,315 --> 01:07:29,550
But I should be better

962
01:07:31,451 --> 01:07:33,487
than those who choose not to act
as a human when they can.

963
01:07:33,921 --> 01:07:35,756
I am honest about my feelings.

964
01:07:35,756 --> 01:07:37,191
All nobles are like that.

965
01:07:38,592 --> 01:07:39,760
There are many nobles

966
01:07:41,461 --> 01:07:43,530
of great virtue in the world.

967
01:07:44,498 --> 01:07:47,801
My grandmother was noble,
and so was my father-in-law.

968
01:07:48,302 --> 01:07:50,804
Who is your grandmother?
Who is your father-in-law?

969
01:07:50,804 --> 01:07:52,673
You are not Ok Tae Young.

970
01:07:52,973 --> 01:07:54,808
You are just a fake.

971
01:07:54,808 --> 01:07:56,877
Yes, I am a fake.

972
01:07:56,877 --> 01:07:57,978
That is true.

973
01:07:58,545 --> 01:08:00,848
Thanks to you,
it was easy to live as a fake.

974
01:08:00,848 --> 01:08:03,283
I learned so much in your place.

975
01:08:04,051 --> 01:08:05,552
For that, I am grateful.

976
01:08:11,291 --> 01:08:12,726
What a shame for you.

977
01:08:13,660 --> 01:08:15,896
Now you are just a lowly maggot again.

978
01:08:17,397 --> 01:08:18,966
From now on,

979
01:08:19,266 --> 01:08:22,002
until the day you die, I am your master.

980
01:08:22,002 --> 01:08:23,003
My master

981
01:08:24,805 --> 01:08:26,406
is not you.

982
01:08:26,406 --> 01:08:29,376
What, are you going to say
you are your own master?

983
01:08:29,376 --> 01:08:30,978
If I have a master,

984
01:08:32,212 --> 01:08:34,648
it is Lady Tae Young,
who gave me a name,

985
01:08:36,049 --> 01:08:37,384
a dream, and her life.

986
01:08:37,384 --> 01:08:39,186
Do you want to die that badly?

987
01:08:39,720 --> 01:08:42,556
- Shall I cripple your leg?
- Penal Code, Article 337,

988
01:08:43,090 --> 01:08:45,859
assaulting or killing a servant
earns 100 lashes.

989
01:08:46,460 --> 01:08:47,895
Could you survive that?

990
01:08:51,532 --> 01:08:52,866
Lord Kim Nak Soo

991
01:08:54,368 --> 01:08:56,570
could not even withstand 30.

992
01:09:01,141 --> 01:09:02,509
How dare you say that

993
01:09:03,477 --> 01:09:05,579
after getting my father killed!

994
01:09:05,579 --> 01:09:07,047
The one who caused his death

995
01:09:09,650 --> 01:09:11,084
was none other

996
01:09:12,486 --> 01:09:13,887
than your husband, Lord Bak Jun Gi.

997
01:09:16,089 --> 01:09:16,924
What?

998
01:09:16,924 --> 01:09:20,260
He chose the most disposable person
to take the fall.

999
01:09:20,894 --> 01:09:22,930
Someone to cut loose
when things go wrong.

1000
01:09:22,930 --> 01:09:27,034
- Shut up!
- You were just a hostage.

1001
01:09:27,034 --> 01:09:28,969
When Kim Nak Soo was captured,

1002
01:09:28,969 --> 01:09:31,672
you were held as leverage so he couldn't
reveal Bak Jun Gi was behind all of it.

1003
01:09:39,746 --> 01:09:41,782
No matter how much you talk,

1004
01:09:42,783 --> 01:09:44,952
you are still the woman
who killed her husband.

1005
01:09:45,652 --> 01:09:47,287
Because of someone like you,

1006
01:09:47,754 --> 01:09:49,690
Master Seo In will face execution!

1007
01:09:55,095 --> 01:09:56,330
Don't worry.

1008
01:09:57,698 --> 01:09:59,733
I will join him in death soon.

1009
01:10:05,572 --> 01:10:07,241
I am infected with a strange disease.

1010
01:10:10,143 --> 01:10:11,111
Darn it.

1011
01:11:02,396 --> 01:11:04,097
Please spare me.

1012
01:11:04,097 --> 01:11:05,666
Wait, just a moment.

1013
01:11:37,231 --> 01:11:38,232
Thank you.

1014
01:13:26,840 --> 01:13:31,411
=The Tale of Lady Ok=

1015
01:13:32,679 --> 01:13:36,250
I now begin to write my final story.

1016
01:13:37,384 --> 01:13:38,585
This is not a tale

1017
01:13:38,986 --> 01:13:41,488
of a sorrowful woman
mourning her husband.

1018
01:13:42,956 --> 01:13:46,593
This is a tale of a noble legal advocate

1019
01:13:47,027 --> 01:13:50,564
who was born a servant
but resilient like aloe

1020
01:13:50,564 --> 01:13:53,567
who stayed strong and helped others.

1021
01:13:55,469 --> 01:13:57,437
I trust this tale's end

1022
01:13:57,437 --> 01:13:59,940
will be filled
with how you will do, my love.

1023
01:14:00,607 --> 01:14:01,875
From your husband.
